data.name: materialLabel7.Text
data.value: Warning: when changing layouts you should always use an SZS with the original layout (bg doesn't matter), if the layout in the SZS you opened has already been modified, either manually or with this tool, the new layout may behave incorrectly.

data.name: tbPatches.Text
data.value:
Frequently asked questions:
Q: How to install themes? A: You need the NXThemes Installer homebrew, you can get it from GitHub: https://github.com/exelix11/SwitchThemeInjector/releases (it's the NRO file) it can install both nxtheme and szs files.
Q: How to make custom layouts? A: Check out Switch Layout Editor: https://github.com/FuryBaguette/SwitchLayoutEditor/wiki
Q: I installed a bad theme and now the console won't boot anymore, how to fix it? A: Delete the '0100000000001000' and '0100000000001013' folders in 'SDcard:/<your cfw>/titles' or contents if using latest atmosphere.
